member.summary:
Represents the behavior for control value set by executing  behavior first;
then, if value to set is not  or empty,
executes  behavior.

summary.para:
Executable script:

var currentValue = arguments[0].value;
arguments[0].value = currentValue ? currentValue + arguments[1] : arguments[1];

Executable script:

arguments[0].value = arguments[1];
arguments[0].dispatchEvent(new Event('change'));

