arguments[0].dispatchEvent(new Event('change'));

member.summary:
            Fills the template string with variables of this  instance.
            The  can contain variables wrapped with curly braces, e.g. "{varName}".
            Variables support standard .NET formatting ("{numberVar:D5}" or "{dateTimeVar:yyyy-MM-dd}")
            and extended formatting for strings
            (for example, "{stringVar:/*}" appends "/" to the beginning of the string, if variable is not null).


